<h3>Hindu way of life</h3>
<p>1. S Radhakrishnan -- People on right side of Sindhu are Hindu as called by persians.</p>
<p>2. SC -- hindusim is a way of life.</p>
<p>3. Monier Williams HIstorian -- Hinduism is not a mere theism resting on Brahminism. It represents complex interaction and gradual accumulation of cultural elements throughout history. It reflects the composite character of Hindus who are not one people but many.</p>